+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01M1VZ9PXfHfaAKgY7wqggV4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01FYsTKSkpqaewNQoH3bNy9f","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"node -e \"\n// Performance analysis:\n// For numFree = 30 in solveToggle's meet-in-middle:\n// half1 = 15, half2 = 15\n// Building firstHalfDeltas: 2^15 = 32768 bigint values. Fast.\n// Building secondHalfDeltas: 2^15 = 32768 bigint values. Fast.\n// Main loop: 32768 * 32768 = 1,073,741,824 iterations.\n// Each iteration: one bigint XOR, one popcount (on a ~40-bit number), one comparison.\n// popcount on bigints: uses Brian Kernighan's algorithm, O(weight) per call.\n// For a 40-bit number, average weight is 20, so ~20 iterations of bigint ops per popcount.\n//\n// 1B iterations * ~20 bigint ops each = ~20B bigint operations.\n// BigInt operations in V8 are relatively slow (not optimized like regular numbers).\n// A rough estimate: ~50ns per bigint operation -> 20B * 50ns = 1000 seconds. WAY TOO SLOW!\n//\n// Even with faster bigint ops (~10ns), 20B * 10ns = 200 seconds. Still too slow.\n//\n// The direct enumeration path (numFree <= 24) has 2^24 ~ 16.7M iterations.\n// Each with a bigint delta computation (loop over numFree bits ~ 24 ops) + popcount.\n// 16.7M * 50 ops ~ 838M bigint ops. At 50ns each = ~42 seconds. Also potentially tight!\n//\n// The meet-in-middle avoids the delta computation by precomputing, so it's just:\n// XOR + popcount + comparison per iteration. But 1B iterations with bigint popcount\n// is still very expensive.\n//\n// For numFree=24, the direct path: 2^24 = 16.7M. With ~24 bigint XOR/check ops per\n// iteration for the delta, plus popcount: could be ~40-80 ops per iteration.\n// 16.7M * 80 * 50ns = 67 seconds. This is concerning.\n//\n// In practice, V8 may optimize bigint operations better than this estimate.\n// The tests pass in 11ms total, but those are small cases.\nconsole.log('Performance could be an issue for numFree >= 24 due to bigint overhead');\nconsole.log('The meet-in-middle for numFree=30 is likely too slow (1B iterations with bigint popcount)');\n\"","description":"Analyze performance characteristics"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":390,"cache_read_input_tokens":42509,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":390},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01RQ7KPPxSPkFnWcu97eUnuS","session_id":"30bb2d9f-5800-4f98-80a0-55c1f0cc75cc","uuid":"6e666294-52f8-40e7-b013-05f4c7f3fb0d"}
